  <brief_title>Air Purifier to Improve Endothelial Function and Carotid Intima Thickness</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Controlled Trial of Air Purifier to Improve Endothelial Function and Carotid Intima Thickness in Older Diabetic People With Cognitive Impairment</official_title>
